Launch the application using the command above.
Enter your name in the "Your Name" field.
Input the amount you want to convert in the "Amount" field.
Select the source currency (e.g., USD) from the "From Currency" dropdown.
Select the target currency (e.g., EUR) from the "To Currency" dropdown.
Click the Convert button to see the result, displayed as: [Your Name], Converted Amount: [Amount] [Target Currency].
If an error occurs (e.g., invalid amount or missing name), a message box will guide you to correct the input.
